<body>
    <h1>eZ Platform 15.12 Release notes</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"contentLayout2">=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h4 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Quicklinks"><span style=3D"color: rgb=
(0,98,147);">Quick links</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"/display/TECHDOC/Installation">Installation instructions</a>=
<a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/ezplatform/blob/v15.05/INSTALL.md" =
class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"></a></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><a href=3D"/display/TECHDOC/Requi=
rements">Requirements</a></span></li>
<li><p>Download: See&nbsp;<a href=3D"http://share.ez.no/downloads/downloads=
/ez-platform-15.12" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">share.ez.no/do=
wnloads</a></p></li>
</ul>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>15.12 is the first stable release of eZ Platform.&nbsp;</p>
<p>These release notes describe the first stable Fast-Track release of eZ P=
latform, as compared to the previous one, 15.11.</p>
<h1 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Highlights">Highlights</h1>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Theezpublishfolderhasbeenrenamedtoapp=
">The&nbsp;<code>ezpublish</code> folder has been renamed to&nbsp;<code>app=
</code></h2>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>The directory that contains the configuration, cache and kernel files ha=
d been named&nbsp;<code>ezpublish</code> since release 5.0. After serious c=
onsideration, it has been renamed to&nbsp;<code>app</code>, in order to be =
closer to the standard Symfony distribution.</p>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Thedefaultinstallationdatahavebeencle=
anedup">The default installation data have been cleaned up</h2>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>Since the removal of the demo in the 2015.11 release, a clean SQL dump i=
s now used to install the system. This dump has been cleaned up, and should=
 now provide you with a very clean basis to start your projects. It contain=
s a few content types (folder, article, image, user group, user), as well a=
s the minimal folders (Content, Media, and Users).</p>
<p>It will be installed when executing&nbsp;<code>php app/console ezplatfor=
m:install clean</code>.</p>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Onlineeditorimprovements">Online edit=
or improvements</h2>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>A new feature made it into the Online Editor: image editing. While the f=
eature is still a bit primitive, it will allow you to embed an image Conten=
t item into a richtext field (<a href=3D"http://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-25108=
" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"><span>EZP-25108</span></a><span>=
).</span></p>
<p>In addition, several issues with the editor were fixed:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>The "add content" toolbar will show up independently of the focus mode =
(<a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-24829" class=3D"external-link" re=
l=3D"nofollow">EZP-24829</a>, <a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-2518=
2" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-25182</a>), will disappear =
when the editor loses focus (<a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-25181=
" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-25181</a>), and will be rend=
ered correctly in IE11/Edge&nbsp;(<a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-=
25189" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-25189</a>)</li>
<li>html5edit input with HTML entities is now accepted (<a href=3D"https://=
jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-24732" style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;" class=3D"exter=
nal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-24732</a>)</li>
<li>Richtext content can now be published with Firefox (<a href=3D"https://=
jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-25161" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-2=
5161</a>)</li>
</ul>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-EnhancedPlatformUIperformanceswiththe=
comboloader">Enhanced PlatformUI performances with the combo loader</h2>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>The assets used by PlatformUI will now be combined into a couple large f=
iles. This drastically reduces the amount of HTTP queries required to load =
the UI, resulting in a much shorter loading time.</p>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-Universaldiscoverywidgetsearchinterfa=
ce">Universal discovery widget search interface</h2>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<p>A search form has been added to the universal discovery widget. Combined=
 with the tree based navigation, this makes <span>locating content in the t=
ree easier than before.</span></p>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12Releasenotes-RESTAPI">REST API</h2>
<p>The REST API views will now include the total number of search hits.</p>
</div>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">=20
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">=20
<div class=3D"innerCell">=20
